    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Note that while the AI itself does not have any difficulty settings, you can still make it easier for you to fight it by tweaking some game options:\r\n\r\n* Choose the lowest amount of starting cash. Do *not* make the mistake and choose the highest in the hopes that it will give you an advantage. The AI will make better use of the money and will annihilate you within minutes.\r\n* Disable starting units\r\n* Choose small maps."
  },
