    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Mission difficulty settings is the responsibility of the scripter, and can be introduced to a mission through a YAML setting. _Actual difficulty adjustments has to be made on **Lua**._\r\n\r\nThe use of a custom Hacky-AIs has been done based on some fan-made maps on the YAML level. Here I used a custom HackyAI to give the AI nuclear powers: http://resource.openra.net/maps/19901/\r\n\r\nHowever, the ability for the difficulty settings to affect other _**YAML**_ settings (e.g. attachment of Hacky-AI to a map player) is probably not there, but this has to be tested.\r\n"
